'CLASS :: bluMouseEvents

'Subclass an object to track mouse enter / leave / wheel events

'Status             Ready to use
'Dependencies       bluMagic.cls
'Last Updated       17-AUG-13
'Last Update        `WM_MOUSEMOVE` added twice when subclassing

